    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with individual throttle bodies. This example exhibits strong mid-range torque and a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS rebuild and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure long-term chassis integrity. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise gate selection, paired with a functional M-Variable Differential Lock for optimal traction. The suspension geometry remains true, featuring refreshed bushings and an upgraded cooling system to manage thermal loads during spirited driving. A focused machine for the discerning enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain health and structural rigidity.",
