      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a well-maintained example of its model, balancing daily utility with a high standard of care. The exterior is finished in its original factory paint, which still holds a deep, reflective shine; however, close inspection will reveal a few light stone chips on the hood and minor scuffing on the rear bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is in excellent shape, featuring leather upholstery that remains supple with only minor creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic components, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and infotainment system, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent professional inspection confirming that the engine and transmission are in great working order. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced just last season. We have a complete folder of service receipts to provide the next owner with total peace of mind.",
